# No Cursor Branding in PRs

Never include "Made with Cursor", "Generated by Cursor", or any similar Cursor branding/attribution text in:

- PR descriptions / body
- PR titles
- Commit messages (including git trailers like `Made-with: Cursor`)
- Code comments
- Issue descriptions
